abstract = {Scholarship in the humanities often requires the ability to search curated electronic corpora and to display search results in a variety of formats. Challenges that need to be addressed include transforming the texts into a suitable form, typically XML, and catering to the scholars' search and display needs. We describe our experience in creating such a search and display facility.},
